{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602290/extras/EA_TH3M15_Guild_About_Img1_v1.png?t=1730496265\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deploy into battle as the TH3-M15 Guild, the deadliest group of mercenaries across the land! Hauntingly, there exists no reported sightings on any of the active members, making the people wonder if the guild even exists. Those that do know them, are either in awe or in fear of the guild\u2019s prowess and efficiency. With the world now at war, between the Aigam Council and Phian Federation, TH3-M15 guild has once again been hired and is on the move. They\u2019ll do whatever it takes to complete their mission\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this rogue-lite, bullet hell game, players will undertake dangerous assignments, fighting off armies of robots and creatures alike. Use an arsenal of unique skills, weapons, and items to mow down your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you have what it takes to finish the job, mercenary?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602290/extras/Mission_gif_v2.gif?t=1730496265\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Go into battle in uniquely created maps, against hordes of enemies and bosses. Each map will have its own hazards and mechanics to give players a great challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight an array of bosses, all with their own special designs and attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn and loot a diverse set of weapons, armors, and items to strengthen your mercenary.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Overdrive your skills and weapons, evolving the carnage to the next level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mix and match your favorite mercenaries with your best weapons together for endless possibilities!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"1st Assignment","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602290/ac4fd35f94edf430415b7760d67098845edc4054.jpg"},{"name":"My Lucky Coin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602290/03d8925a9e4e3e4325854170d12d19b1485aba3e.jpg"},{"name":"Full Pocket","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602290/229ede2e493b87bd14f5343c1704f093d45773c3.jpg"},{"name":"Fatal Strike","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602290/a03b7283ffd7d3019ef06e27ba0a9403e9a260a6.jpg"},{"name":"Mighty Sponge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602290/cf755bd4c46b851c59448ecb22f9a7bc69a151e7.jpg"},{"name":"Lightly Dressed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602290/882269d1f03254d23ee36af0d2817ccb233dc9e5.jpg"},{"name":"Dressed Appropriately","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602290/997ecf39f9b11f47777463d1daf2f104d42cb0a7.jpg"},{"name":"Fully Decked Out!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602290/abc9a57e75ddea5914dc670dc2e45e037a93d722.jpg"},{"name":"Dressed 2 Kill","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602290/0b8c572e3940c9887d841ccc92d53a7325d4d604.jpg"},{"name":"This is Vandalism!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2602290/1dacfb98b7bcc17899dd174dc5edde2da4f88149.jpg"}],"total":61},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730496265","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app